amazon_product_info.description: Product Description Stardrops White Vinegar Spray is a multi-purpose cleaning solution that is effective on limescale, and can also be used for general stain removal. The hard working formula is ideal for cleaning glass, mirrors, laundry and most other surfaces around the home. The use of vinegar as a cleaning agent has been used for years as a gentle way of removing stains from fabrics and surfaces. Vinegar has also been a popular cleaning product for windows and glass, as it leaves a clear, streak free finish. Stardrops White Vinegar Spray is produced using acetic acid, the main compound found in vinegar which allows it to mimic the multiple cleaning abilities of traditional vinegar, but comes complete in an easy to use spray bottle for convenient cleaning around the home.
